      <p begin="00:55.310" end="01:01.330" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:55.310" end="00:56.000">Why</span> <span begin="00:56.000" end="00:56.460">ha</span><span begin="00:56.460" end="00:56.550">ve</span> <span begin="00:56.550" end="00:56.960">you</span> <span begin="00:56.960" end="00:57.120">f</span><span begin="00:57.120" end="00:57.500">or</span><span begin="00:57.500" end="00:57.780">s</span><span begin="00:57.780" end="00:59.670">a</span><span begin="00:59.670" end="00:59.970">ken</span> <span begin="00:59.970" end="01:01.330">us?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为何您要将我们无情抛弃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">為何您要將我們無情拋棄</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">何故我らを見捨てたのか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어찌하여 우리를 버리셨나이까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pourquoi nous as-tu abandonnées ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Por qué nos has abandonado?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warum hast du uns verlassen?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por que você nos abandonou?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему ты оставила нас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Perché ci hai abbandonati</span></p>
      <p begin="01:02.520" end="01:10.920" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="01:02.520" end="01:03.120">Mo</span><span begin="01:03.120" end="01:03.700">ther</span> <span begin="01:03.700" end="01:04.310">of</span> <span begin="01:04.310" end="01:04.680">thi</span><span begin="01:04.680" end="01:04.930">s</span> <span begin="01:04.930" end="01:05.570">sa</span><span begin="01:05.570" end="01:05.920">cred</span> <span begin="01:06.160" end="01:06.600">dream</span> <span begin="01:06.750" end="01:07.100">that</span> <span begin="01:07.340" end="01:09.240">burn</span><span begin="01:09.240" end="01:09.340">s</span> <span begin="01:09.340" end="01:09.610">in</span> <span begin="01:09.610" end="01:10.920">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">致那孕育了 在我们心中熊熊燃烧的神圣之梦的慈母</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">致那孕育了 在我們心中熊熊燃燒的神聖之夢的慈母</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">我らの中で燃えるこの聖なる夢の母よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리 안에서 타오르는 이 성스러운 꿈의 어머니시여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mère de ce rêve sacré qui brûle en nous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Madre de este sueño sagrado que arde en nosotros</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mutter dieses heiligen Traums der in uns brennt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mãe deste sonho sagrado que queima em nós</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Матерь этого священного сна что горит в нас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Madre di questo sacro sogno che brucia in noi</span></p>
      <p begin="01:12.140" end="01:21.100" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="01:12.140" end="01:12.850">Will</span> <span begin="01:12.850" end="01:13.290">you</span> <span begin="01:13.360" end="01:13.990">hear</span> <span begin="01:13.990" end="01:14.540">our</span> <span begin="01:14.540" end="01:15.150">voi</span><span begin="01:15.150" end="01:15.750">ces</span> <span begin="01:15.750" end="01:16.270">ma</span><span begin="01:16.380" end="01:16.460">ke</span> <span begin="01:16.460" end="01:16.730">u</span><span begin="01:16.730" end="01:16.950">s</span> <span begin="01:16.950" end="01:18.970">glo</span><span begin="01:18.970" end="01:19.340">ri</span><span begin="01:19.340" end="01:21.100">ous?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">您能否听见我们的呼唤 赐予我们无上的荣耀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">您能否聽見我們的呼喚 賜予我們無上的榮耀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">我らの声を聞き栄光を与えてくれるのか</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리의 목소리를 들으시어 우릴 영광되게 하시렵니까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Entendras-tu nos voix pour nous rendre glorieuses ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Escucharás nuestras voces hacernos gloriosos?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wirst du unsere Stimmen hören uns glorreich machen?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você ouvirá nossas vozes nos fará gloriosas?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Услышишь ли ты наши голоса одаришь ли нас величием</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ascolterai le nostre voci rendici gloriosi</span></p>
