      <p begin="02:00.120" end="02:08.320" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="02:00.120" end="02:00.630">Mo</span><span begin="02:00.760" end="02:01.400">ther</span> <span begin="02:01.400" end="02:01.800">o</span><span begin="02:01.800" end="02:01.870">f</span> <span begin="02:02.020" end="02:02.340">thi</span><span begin="02:02.340" end="02:02.450">s</span> <span begin="02:02.520" end="02:02.970">cur</span><span begin="02:03.120" end="02:03.620">sed</span> <span begin="02:03.770" end="02:04.280">ra</span><span begin="02:04.280" end="02:04.420">ge</span> <span begin="02:04.470" end="02:04.810">that</span> <span begin="02:05.050" end="02:06.840">burn</span><span begin="02:06.840" end="02:06.950">s</span> <span begin="02:06.950" end="02:07.170">in</span> <span begin="02:07.170" end="02:08.320">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">致那孕育了 在我们心中熊熊燃烧的受诅狂怒的慈母</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">致那孕育了 在我們心中熊熊燃燒的受詛狂怒的慈母</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">我らの中で燃えるこの呪われた怒りの母よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리 안에서 타오르는 이 저주받은 분노의 어머니시여</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mère de cette rage maudite qui brûle en nous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Madre de esta rabia maldita que arde en nosotros</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mutter dieses verfluchten Zorns der in uns brennt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mãe desta raiva amaldiçoada que queima em nós</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Матерь этой проклятой ярости что горит в нас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Madre di questa rabbia maledetta che brucia in noi</span></p>
      <p begin="02:35.640" end="02:36.840" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="02:35.640" end="02:35.730">I</span> <span begin="02:35.780" end="02:35.880">ju</span><span begin="02:35.880" end="02:35.970">st</span> <span begin="02:36.060" end="02:36.220">want</span> <span begin="02:36.220" end="02:36.290">to</span> <span begin="02:36.360" end="02:36.510">wa</span><span begin="02:36.590" end="02:36.680">ke</span> <span begin="02:36.680" end="02:36.840">up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我只想要从这梦中醒来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我只想要從這夢中醒來</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ただ目を覚ましたい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그저 깨어나고 싶어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux juste me réveiller</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo quiero despertar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will einfach nur aufwachen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu só quero acordar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я просто хочу проснуться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio solo svegliarmi</span></p>
