      <p begin="02:49.360" end="02:58.720" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:49.360" end="02:49.990">Sing</span> <span begin="02:49.990" end="02:50.490">our</span> <span begin="02:50.490" end="02:51.170">hearts</span> <span begin="02:51.170" end="02:51.730">a</span><span begin="02:51.730" end="02:53.660">wa</span><span begin="02:53.660" end="02:53.720">ke</span> <span begin="02:53.720" end="02:53.980">in</span> <span begin="02:53.980" end="02:55.580">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">用歌声唤醒我们 沉睡的心灵吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">用歌聲喚醒我們 沉睡的心靈吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">歌で我らの心を目覚めさせて</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">우리 마음이 깨어나도록 노래하소서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Chante pour éveiller nos cœurs en nous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Canta hasta despertar nuestros corazones</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Singe unsere Herzen in uns wach</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Cante nossos corações despertos em nós</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пробуди песней наши сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Risveglia col canto i nostri cuori in noi</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:53.970" end="02:58.720"><span begin="02:53.970" end="02:54.160">(F</span><span begin="02:54.160" end="02:54.850">loa</span><span begin="02:54.850" end="02:55.190">ting</span> <span begin="02:55.270" end="02:55.390">th</span><span begin="02:55.390" end="02:55.950">rough</span> <span begin="02:55.950" end="02:56.270">the</span> <span begin="02:56.270" end="02:56.620">s</span><span begin="02:56.620" end="02:58.720">ky)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">漂浮着穿越 这片无垠苍穹</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">漂浮著穿越 這片無垠蒼穹</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">空を漂いながら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하늘을 부유하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Flottant à travers le ciel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Flotando por el cielo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schwebend durch den Himmel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Flutuando pelo céu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Паря в небесах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fluttuando nel cielo</span></span></p>
      <p begin="02:58.870" end="03:07.050" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:58.870" end="02:59.510">See</span> <span begin="02:59.510" end="02:59.860">the</span> <span begin="02:59.860" end="03:00.110">s</span><span begin="03:00.110" end="03:00.590">tar</span><span begin="03:00.590" end="03:00.700">s</span> <span begin="03:00.770" end="03:01.380">they</span> <span begin="03:01.380" end="03:03.130">yearn</span> <span begin="03:03.130" end="03:03.290">f</span><span begin="03:03.290" end="03:03.580">or</span> <span begin="03:03.580" end="03:04.990">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">看那漫天星辰 它们正向我们发出渴求</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">看那漫天星辰 它們正向我們發出渴求</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">星々が我らを渇望するのを見て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">별들이 우리를 갈망하는 것을 보소서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Vois les étoiles elles languissent pour nous</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mira las estrellas anhelan por nosotros</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sieh die Sterne sie sehnen sich nach uns</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Veja as estrelas elas anseiam por nós</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смотри как звезды тоскуют по нам</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Guarda le stelle anelano a noi</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="03:04.060" end="03:07.050"><span begin="03:04.060" end="03:04.990">(Mee</span><span begin="03:04.990" end="03:05.110">t</span> <span begin="03:05.110" end="03:06.140">us</span> <span begin="03:06.370" end="03:07.050">here)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就在此地与我们相见吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就在此地與我們相見吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ここで我らに会って</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이곳에서 우릴 맞이하소서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Rejoins-nous ici</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Encuéntranos aquí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Begegne uns hier</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Encontre-nos aqui</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Встреть нас здесь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Incontraci qui</span></span></p>
